Package: TwoRegression
Type: Package
Title: Process Accelerometer Data with Two-Regression Algorithms
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person(c("Paul", "R."), "Hibbing", email = "paulhibbing@gmail.com",
		  role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Application of Various Two-Regression Algorithms for Accelerometers.
    It provides an easy way for users to read in their accelerometer data files
    and apply an appropriate two-regression algorithm from the following:
    Crouter et al. (2006, J Appl Physiol);
    Crouter et al. (2010, Med Sci Sports Exerc);
    Hibbing et al. (2018, Med Sci Sports Exerc).
